    <p class="tagline">Send heartfelt notes to your loved ones, safely and securely.</p>
</header>

<section class="description">
    <h2>About the App</h2>
    <p>Note-E-Izhaar lets you create personalized notes with messages and photos for someone special. Each note is
        delivered through a unique link containing a secure key encoded in the URL. Only anyone with that URL can view
        the note.</p>
    <button id="create-note-btn">Create Now</button>
    <button id="open-demo-btn">See Demo <i class="fa fa-external-link"></i> </button>
</section>

<section class="encryption-note">
    <h2>Security & Privacy</h2>
    <p>All messages and photos are encrypted end-to-end before being stored in our database. The encryption key is
        encoded in the URL itself. This means that while your data remains encrypted on our servers, anyone with the URL
        can decrypt and view it. We never access your messages or photos directly.</p>
    <p><strong>Note:</strong> Your notes remain stored indefinitely, so your loved ones can revisit them anytime.</p>
</section>

<section class="faqs">
    <h2>FAQs</h2>
    <div class="faq">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-lock"></i>
        <p><strong>Who can read my note?</strong> Anyone with the unique URL containing the encoded key can view the
            note. Make sure to share it only with the intended recipient.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-database"></i>
        <p><strong>Is my note stored permanently?</strong> Yes! Notes remain in our database forever, but they are
            encrypted.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-eye-slash"></i>
        <p><strong>Can anyone else see my note?</strong> No, the server stores only encrypted data. Only someone with
            the URL can decrypt and view the content.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-shield"></i>
        <p><strong>How secure is this?</strong> The note is encrypted using AES-GCM. As long as the URL is private, your
            message is secure from anyone else.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="get-started" style="display:none;">
    <h2>Create Your Note</h2>

    <div class="note-input-container">
        <!-- Text notes will be inserted here -->
        <div class="note-item" draggable="true" data-type="text">
            <span class="drag-handle" title="Drag to reorder">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-grip-lines"></i>
            </span>
            <input type="text" class="note-text-input" placeholder="Type your message here..." />
            <button type="button" class="delete-note-btn" title="Delete note">Ã—</button>
        </div>

        <!-- Photo is always at the bottom -->
        <div id="photo-container"></div>

        <div class="buttons-row">
            <button type="button" id="add-note-btn">Add Note</button>
            <button type="button" id="add-photo-btn">Upload Photo</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="submit-container">
        <button type="button" id="submit-note-btn">Submit Note</button>
    </div>

    <div id="result-container" style="display:none; margin-top:30px; text-align:center;">
        <p>Your note is ready! Share it with this link:</p>

        <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; gap:12px; margin:15px 0; flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <input type="text" id="share-link" readonly
                style="flex:1; min-width:250px; padding:10px 14px; border-radius:8px; border:1px solid #6414e9; font-family:monospace; font-size:0.95rem;">
            <button type="button" id="copy-link-btn"
                style="padding:10px 18px; background:#6414e9; color:#fff; border:none; border-radius:8px; font-weight:600; cursor:pointer;">
                Copy
            </button>
            <button type="button" id="open-link-btn"
                style="padding:10px 18px; background:#6414e9; color:#fff; border:none; border-radius:8px; font-weight:600; cursor:pointer;">
                Open <i class="fa fa-external-link" style="margin-left:6px;"></i>
            </button>
        </div>

        <p style="font-size:0.9rem; color:#555;">
            Anyone with this link can view the note.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>



